<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνωνι χαίρειν Πεττυκᾶμις ὁ κεραμεὺς ἀφ᾽ Ἱερᾶς Νήσου. πεῖραν <choice><corr>μέν</corr><sic>μεμ</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="2"/>μου εἴληφας εἴτε εἰμὶ τεχνίτης εἴτε καὶ οὔ. ἵνα οὖν, εἰ μέλλω ἐργάζεσθαι, 

    <lb n="3"/>ἀναγκαῖόν με τοὺς τεχνίτας τοὺς μέλλοντάς μοι εἶναι χρησίμους κατίσχειν 

    <lb n="4"/>μετ᾽ ἐμαυτοῦ. προσπαραλήψομαι δὲ καὶ Παῆσιν καὶ τοὺς υἱοὺς αὐτοῦ· 

    <lb n="5"/>δοκιμάζω γὰρ αὐτούς, ἅμα δὲ καὶ τῆς γῆς τῆς ἐνταῦθα οὐκ <choice><corr>ἄπειροί</corr><sic>απιροι</sic></choice> εἰσιν. 

    <lb n="6"/>ὥρα δέ ἐστιν ἐργάζεσθαι ἀπὸ τοῦ Θῶυθ, ἵνα τὰ ἔργα χωρίς τε συντελεσ-

    <lb n="7"/>θῇ ἐν ὥραι καὶ ἅμα χρήσιμα.  εὐτύχει. 

    <lb n="8"/>καὶ τὸν τόπον <choice><corr>κέλευσόν</corr><sic>κελευσομ</sic></choice> μοι παραδεῖξαι ἐν ὧι ἐργῶμαι. </ab></div><div n="meta.1138" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1138" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-226" notBefore="-275" type="textDate">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1138" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Datierung nach dem Rahmen des Zenon - Archivs.</p></div><div n="meta.1138" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59500</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1138</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59500</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;3;59500" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1138" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Pl. XXIV</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.1138" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="de"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl default="NO" type="translations">Mees, Organisationsformen römischer Töpfer-Manufakturen (2002), S. 367</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1138" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" full="yes" type="ancientFindspot">Hiera Nesos</placeName